software.

The following software/libraries are used in Wrapl/Riva:

The Hans-Boehm garbage collector:
	http://www.hpl.hp.com/personal/Hans_Boehm/gc/
The libconfuse configuration file parser:
	http://www.nongnu.org/confuse/
The GNU MP Bignum library:
	http://gmplib.org/
The Lua programming language:
	http://www.lua.org/
Ben Pfaff's GNU libavl:
	http://www.stanford.edu/~blp/avl/
